Package by.kovalenko.periodicals.command

Interface Summary
ICommand Interface ICommand is base interface for all classes, which can be submitted a request.
 

Class Summary
EditionAddToCartCommand Class EditionAddToCartCommand is used for adding edition to user cart.
EditionCreateCommand Class EditionCreateCommand is used for creating edition.
EditionDeleteCommand Class EditionDeleteCommand is used for deleting edition.
EditionDeleteFromCartCommand Class EditionDeleteFromCartCommand is used for deleting edition from user's cart.
EditionEditCommand Class EditionEditCommand is used for editing editions.
EditionListCommand Class EditionListCommand is used to display a list of existing editions.
EditionSaveCommand Class EditionSaveCommand is used to save an created existing edition.
EditionUpdateCommand Class EditionUpdateCommand is used to update an edited existing edition.
ErrorCommand Class ErrorCommand is used to generate error JSP-page.
UserAddCartToSubscriptionsCommand Class UserAddCartToSubscriptionsCommand is used for adding editions of the users's cart to the list of subscriptions.
UserCreateCommand Class UserCreateCommand is used for creating user.
UserDeleteCommand Class UserDeleteCommand is used for deleting user.
UserEditCommand Class UserEditCommand is used for editing users.
UserGetCartCommand Class UserGetCartCommand is used to display user's cart .
